{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"909ccc6dba","title":"毛泽东会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","origin":"外交部绝密文件，文特43","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9a8210599","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"909ccc6dba"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7d0311c4b","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）毛泽东（未经本人审阅）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"909ccc6dba"},{"id":"58831842f1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫做发展中的国家。你不要看中国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，I SAY（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"909ccc6dba"},{"id":"a337f7eba8","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化──包括语言──的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"909ccc6dba"},{"id":"d3f774279d","type":"paragraph","text":"（外交部绝密文件，文特43）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"909ccc6dba"}],"page":{"id":"4bc0aed8b9","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"909ccc6dba","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}